==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Magnetomotive
<hw>Mag`net*o*mo"tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Magneto-</ets> + <ets>motive</ets>, a.]</ety>
<fld>(Elec.)</fld> <def>Pertaining to, or designating, a force producing
magnetic flux, analogous to electromotive force, and equal to the
magnetic flux multiplied by the magnetic reluctance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>magnetomotive force</ent>⟦br⟧
